room_title: Escape room "Tony's Bistro" by MindGames of Mebane in Mebane
room_description: Notorious hitman, Rocco Roselli, has been murdered at Tony’s Bistro. Help the FBI and local law enforcement solve the murder, and find the money and a ledger detailing the criminal activity of the city. Now, collect a team of top organized crime investigators and come to Tony’s Bistro.
